Partner in crime, my built-in best friend, and the ultimate co-conspirator in all our brilliantly bad decisions! From laughing at our failures to hyping each other up for the next adventure, there’s no one else I’d rather have by my side to take on the world (and occasionally mess things up). Life wouldn’t be half as fun without you causing chaos with me. Here’s to all the questionable choices, endless laughs, and unforgettable memories we’ve created together. Love you forever, my sister, my ride-or-die! 💕👯‍♀️
